{"id":638683,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/【朋友圈】郑也夫、王瑛呼吁给失联的任志强一/","date":"2020-03-15T20:46:02Z","modified":"2020-03-17T00:05:51Z","title":"【朋友圈】郑也夫、王瑛呼吁给失联的任志强“一个说法”","content":"<p>CDT编者按：近日，据传<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e3%80%90%e6%9c%8b%e5%8f%8b%e5%9c%88%e3%80%91%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%e8%a2%ab%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e5%b8%82%e7%ba%aa%e5%a7%94%e7%95%99%e7%bd%ae%e8%b0%88%e8%af%9d/\">任志强被北京市纪委留置谈话</a>，其原因是前不久他的写一篇文章<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%9a%84%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e8%a2%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e7%97%85%e5%85%b1%e5%90%8c%e4%bc%a4%e5%ae%b3/\">《任志强：人民的生命被病毒和体制的重病共同伤害》</a>。在文章中，任志强批评了中共专制体制对疫情防治工作的破坏作用，并称习近平“是一位剥光了衣服也要坚持当皇帝的小丑”。这两日，任志强仍无确切的消息。3月14日，北京大学教授郑也夫给任志强亲属发出公开信，希望任志强家属可以迅速向社会通报任志强的消息，“或清除谣言，或促进社会与当局的互动”。任志强的朋友王瑛也在朋友圈发声，要求为失联已经失去72小时的任志强“一个正式的说法”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638684\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"814\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-13.jpg 987w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-13-184x300.jpg 184w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-13-629x1024.jpg 629w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-13-768x1250.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-13-944x1536.jpg 944w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638685\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7.jpg 1125w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-7-1080x2339.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"SvfjjsFy6v\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e3%80%90%e6%9c%8b%e5%8f%8b%e5%9c%88%e3%80%91%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%e8%a2%ab%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e5%b8%82%e7%ba%aa%e5%a7%94%e7%95%99%e7%bd%ae%e8%b0%88%e8%af%9d/\">【朋友圈】任志强被北京市纪委留置谈话</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【朋友圈】任志强被北京市纪委留置谈话》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e3%80%90%e6%9c%8b%e5%8f%8b%e5%9c%88%e3%80%91%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%e8%a2%ab%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e5%b8%82%e7%ba%aa%e5%a7%94%e7%95%99%e7%bd%ae%e8%b0%88%e8%af%9d/embed/#?secret=SvfjjsFy6v\" data-secret=\"SvfjjsFy6v\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"ARkYV8wGTw\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%9a%84%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e8%a2%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e7%97%85%e5%85%b1%e5%90%8c%e4%bc%a4%e5%ae%b3/\">任志强：人民的生命被病毒和体制的重病共同伤害</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《任志强：人民的生命被病毒和体制的重病共同伤害》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e4%bb%bb%e5%bf%97%e5%bc%ba%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%9a%84%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e8%a2%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e7%97%85%e5%85%b1%e5%90%8c%e4%bc%a